	<div style="text-align:right;">
		LOBO, Gustavo Schehceli<sup>1</sup>; COSTA, Leandro Batista<sup>2</sup>; ENGRACIA FILHO, Jair Rodini<sup>3</sup>; JESUS, Rebecca Mayre Miranda de<sup>4</sup>; SCHOEMBERGER, Adrielle Cristina<sup>5</sup>; MAITO, Camilla de Marco<sup>6</sup>; ANDRADE, Carla de<sup>7</sup>		<BR>
